RSH (Remote Shell) : port 514
SMB (Server Message Block) : port 445
SQL (Structured Query Language) : port 1433
VNC (Virtual Network Computing) : ports 5900-5903
NFS (Network File System) : port 2049
SIP (Session Initiation Protocol) : port 5060
RTP (Real-time Transport Protocol) : ports 16384-32767
IPSec (Internet Protocol Security) : ports 500 et 4500
PPTP (Point-to-Point Tunneling Protocol) : port 1723
L2TP (Layer 2 Tunneling Protocol) : port 1701
-
SOCKS : port 1080
BitTorrent : port 6881-6889
